Package CallOf2D

Class Asset

java.lang.Object
CallOf2D.Asset
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bullet, Enemy, Floor, MedKit, Player, SpeedUp, Wall
public abstract class Asset extends Object
Asset class is a superclass that is used by every entity in the game. It contains methods for getting and setting position values (x & y), movement values (dX & dY), and ID field.
